         <abstract id="aspace_a3ac1f150d83a36ae9fae4f279707924">Letters to the English novelist Stephen McKenna, principally from other authors, including Alfred Austin, Arnold Bennett, John Drinkwater, John Galsworthy, Compton Mackenzie, John Masefield, Arthur Wing Pinero, Frank Swinnerton, Hugh Walpole and Arthur Waugh. Many of the letters concern invitations to literary dinners and other social events.</abstract>
         <origination label="creator">
            <persname source="ingest">
               <part>McKenna, Stephen, 1888-</part>
            </persname>
         </origination>
    
      </did>
